{
  "stem": "6736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And my Mordechai Yehuda went out of the ghetto, and he was in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He was working in the Vistula by people--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Under water the have the barges.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he worked on the barges as a Christian boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ghetto was liquidated on March 13, on a Saturday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for whole week, they were bringing out people from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were some in hospital where they shot the-- the people in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And those who were hidden, those who had no papers, they brought in to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I stayed with the group of workers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because in Plaszow I was working in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is building barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we made sidewalks out of the tombstones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were taken in to do special work to take off the dead bodies and put them in the hole, and later bury them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In one case, we picked up a little girl, a child, and we walked over-- I hold it in my hand and I walked over to the German.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I asked her if she was 3/4 dead, akt der gnadenschuss.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Akt der gnadenschuss means a kindness, a bullet, a kind bullet so the kid will not suffer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And his answer was, for that scheisse, for that piece of shit, it's a schade.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Throw it in the grave alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every night after I finish working, my uncle, who was already in Plaszow, because when they liquidated the ghetto, they took him to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he would ask me did you see familiar faces?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every day when I saw little kids, I turned around not to see was my brother, or my cousin, or somebody that I knew.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
